    <briefdescription>
<para>Abstract interface for loading fonts and providing glyph data. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>`FontResourceProvider` defines the contract for font management in the helios text rendering system. Implementations handle the specifics of loading font files and caching glyph data for efficient text rendering.</para>
<para>## Responsibilities</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>**Font Loading:** Load font files from disk and parse glyph metrics.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>**Glyph Retrieval:** Provide glyph data (texture, metrics) for individual characters.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>**Caching:** Cache loaded glyphs to avoid redundant loading.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="structhelios_1_1rendering_1_1text_1_1Glyph" kindref="compound">Glyph</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
